Requirements:
This project requires the following software:
-MATLAB (R2020a or later recommended)
-Simulink (for model-based simulation, optional)
-Control System Toolbox (for transfer function and system analysis)

Required MATLAB Functions/Toolboxes:
-tf() – Transfer function modeling
-feedback() – Closed-loop system
-step() – Step response analysis
-stepinfo() – Performance metrics
-lsim() – Time-domain simulation with disturbance
